@startuml Student Learning Sequence

participant Student
participant System
participant Database

Student -> System: Login
System -> Database: Authenticate User
Database --> System: User Verified
System --> Student: Login Success

Student -> System: Choose Chapter
System -> Database: Load Chapter Data
Database --> System: Chapter Questions
System --> Student: Display Level

Student -> System: Submit Answer
System -> System: Validate Answer

alt Answer Correct (passes)
    System -> Database: Update Progress
    System -> Database: Award XP
    Database --> System: Progress Saved
    System --> Student: Advance to Next Level
else Answer Incorrect (retries)
    System -> Database: Deduct Heart
    Database --> System: Hearts Updated
    System --> Student: Retry Current Level
end

@enduml